1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,919
=Episode 11=

19
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:13,249
(Get Rich)

20
00:01:13,250 --> 00:01:14,420
Mr. Gu.

21
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:17,049
Since you're so fond of this place,

22
00:01:17,050 --> 00:01:18,450
do come often.

23
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:50,700
What if Yanqiu is a time traveler too?

24
00:01:51,490 --> 00:01:53,140
Could she be up to something?

25
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:57,340
Nice location.

26
00:01:58,020 --> 00:01:59,340
What a shame to waste it.

27
00:02:00,050 --> 00:02:01,650
I'll be frank.

28
00:02:01,850 --> 00:02:03,700
I'm looking to expand.

29
00:02:04,130 --> 00:02:05,170
So,

30
00:02:05,250 --> 00:02:06,420
let's work together.

31
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:10,489
You want to

32
00:02:10,490 --> 00:02:11,740
buy out Xiaoyao Pavilion

33
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:12,740
and become

34
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:14,650
the CEO?

35
00:02:15,650 --> 00:02:16,740
Right.

36
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:19,130
I do intend to acquire it.

37
00:02:21,490 --> 00:02:23,329
Are you offering shares

38
00:02:23,330 --> 00:02:24,340
or stock options?

39
00:02:26,530 --> 00:02:28,220
Cash.

40
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:34,410
I plan to open a gambling house.

41
00:02:34,610 --> 00:02:35,769
This place

42
00:02:35,770 --> 00:02:36,930
has great fengshui.

43
00:02:37,370 --> 00:02:39,180
It's bound to bring in a fortune.

44
00:02:39,370 --> 00:02:40,740
I've even picked a name.

45
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:42,850
"Sha" for prosperity,

46
00:02:42,930 --> 00:02:44,180
"Zhu" for wealth.

47
00:02:44,530 --> 00:02:46,130
To rake in riches,

48
00:02:46,610 --> 00:02:47,970
I'll call it

49
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:48,970
Sha

50
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:49,930
zhu

51
00:02:50,330 --> 00:02:51,250
pan.

52
00:02:52,810 --> 00:02:54,930
- A pig-butchering scam?
- A pig-butchering scam?

53
00:02:58,020 --> 00:02:59,220
Well, Mr. Gu?

54
00:02:59,490 --> 00:03:00,259
Think about it.

55
00:03:00,260 --> 00:03:02,220
No. We don't touch prostitution,
gambling, or drugs.

56
00:03:03,140 --> 00:03:04,850
People say all merchants are crooked.

57
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:05,739
Yet you

58
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:07,970
turned down easy money.

59
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:09,840
I'm impressed.

60
00:03:12,740 --> 00:03:14,250
It's gathering dust.

61
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:15,850
I doubt

62
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:17,500
it'll last another month.

63
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:19,179
If you change your mind,

64
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:20,340
come see me.

65
00:03:20,530 --> 00:03:21,780
Take this money

66
00:03:21,930 --> 00:03:23,500
as a token of my sincerity.

67
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:28,530
A pig-butchering scam.
She has to be a time traveler.

68
00:03:29,370 --> 00:03:30,410
I'm not so sure.

69
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,529
"Sha" for prosperity,

70
00:03:32,530 --> 00:03:33,970
"Zhu" for wealth.

71
00:03:34,090 --> 00:03:35,620
What if she really meant it?

72
00:03:37,090 --> 00:03:38,300
What do we do now?

73
00:03:39,930 --> 00:03:40,620
Gu Bei,

74
00:03:40,770 --> 00:03:42,130
does she have a thing for you too?

75
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:46,209
If business is dead, close the place
and come back with me.

76
00:03:46,210 --> 00:03:47,649
You're not going anywhere.

77
00:03:47,650 --> 00:03:49,650
I've got money. I'll cover any losses.

78
00:03:55,370 --> 00:03:56,250
Enough!

79
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,850
Have you lost faith in me?

80
00:03:58,530 --> 00:03:59,760
Of course not.

81
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,840
Otherwise, I wouldn't have come
to the capital with you.

82
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:04,089
I'm the one who believes in you most.

83
00:04:04,090 --> 00:04:05,060
Otherwise,

84
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:08,180
I wouldn't have entrusted my life to you.

85
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,179
So,

86
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,179
the tougher it gets,

87
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:15,780
the calmer we stay.

88
00:04:16,330 --> 00:04:17,820
And the more united.

89
00:04:18,380 --> 00:04:19,259
I think

90
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:20,700
our problem isn't the product.

91
00:04:20,770 --> 00:04:22,530
We're lacking star power.

92
00:04:22,970 --> 00:04:25,900
The only one
who can save Xiaoyao Pavilion

93
00:04:26,290 --> 00:04:28,380
is Princess Xiao Ling.

94
00:04:31,410 --> 00:04:32,140
Me?

95
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,919
(Xiaoyao Beauty Cream
Approved by the Princess)

96
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,759
(Xiaoyao Beauty Cream)

97
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,680
(Xiaoyao Pavilion)

98
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,440
(Free beer with any purchase)

99
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,700
Ladies and gentlemen,

100
00:04:55,770 --> 00:04:58,699
we're introducing
a brand-new drink today.

101
00:04:58,700 --> 00:04:59,969
Free samples for everyone!

102
00:04:59,970 --> 00:05:00,969
Free samples!

103
00:05:00,970 --> 00:05:02,260
Come on!

104
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:05,169
What is this?

105
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:06,969
It's called beer.
Refreshing and delicious.

106
00:05:06,970 --> 00:05:07,610
Here.

107
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:09,769
Try it.

108
00:05:09,770 --> 00:05:10,619
Rich malt aroma,

109
00:05:10,620 --> 00:05:11,849
smooth finish.

110
00:05:11,850 --> 00:05:12,819
Nice.

111
00:05:12,820 --> 00:05:13,780
You've got taste.

112
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:14,730
Wonderful!

113
00:05:14,850 --> 00:05:15,769
Truly wonderful!

114
00:05:15,770 --> 00:05:16,819
It's even better inside.

115
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:17,499
Come on in!

116
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:18,649
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

117
00:05:18,650 --> 00:05:19,970
- Come on.
- Come on.

118
00:05:21,210 --> 00:05:22,730
Let's raise a glass.

119
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:23,459
Cheers!

120
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:24,700
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

121
00:05:24,850 --> 00:05:25,499
Come on!

122
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:26,969
Easy, everyone. There's plenty.

123
00:05:26,970 --> 00:05:27,780
No rush.

124
00:05:27,970 --> 00:05:30,289
- Don't push.
-Everyone gets one.

125
00:05:30,290 --> 00:05:31,850
- Don't push.
- Here you go.

126
00:05:32,410 --> 00:05:34,170
Take it easy.

127
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,449
Don't crowd from the back.

128
00:05:36,450 --> 00:05:38,000
- One at a time. Everyone gets one.
- Princess Xiao Ling!

129
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,999
I own a hundred mu of land
and five hundred cattle.

130
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,919
I'm loaded.

131
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,699
Please marry me,

132
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,559
Princess Xiao Ling.

133
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,820
Princess Xiao Ling...

134
00:05:44,210 --> 00:05:45,460
Get lost!

135
00:05:45,730 --> 00:05:46,619
Serves you right!

136
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:47,619
What's wrong with you?

137
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:49,900
How dare you harass the Princess!
Asking for a death wish?

138
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:50,850
Get out!

139
00:05:51,850 --> 00:05:53,140
Get out of here!

140
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,120
- We'll settle this later!
- Let's continue.

141
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,919
It's fine.

142
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,670
Here, this one's yours.

143
00:05:59,820 --> 00:06:01,170
Thanks.

144
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:02,729
I thought

145
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:04,380
since we both like Gu Bei,

146
00:06:04,410 --> 00:06:05,820
you'd hate me.

147
00:06:09,290 --> 00:06:10,209
Gu Bei said

148
00:06:10,210 --> 00:06:11,460
that at Xiaoyao Pavilion,

149
00:06:11,730 --> 00:06:13,299
we're one family.

150
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:16,089
You're actually pretty great.

151
00:06:16,090 --> 00:06:17,019
You're honest,

152
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:18,050
straightforward,

153
00:06:18,170 --> 00:06:20,090
and you fight alongside him.

154
00:06:20,330 --> 00:06:21,460
I'm jealous.

155
00:06:25,290 --> 00:06:26,900
You're not bad yourself.

156
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:28,019
Even as a princess,

157
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:29,699
you're not arrogant at all.

158
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:30,619
You even help

159
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:32,020
bring in customers.

160
00:06:32,210 --> 00:06:33,090
I like that.

161
00:06:36,850 --> 00:06:39,290
Gu Bei says this is the highest courtesy
between friends.

162
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:45,769
Hulv!

163
00:06:45,770 --> 00:06:47,089
You're so delicate.

164
00:06:47,090 --> 00:06:48,610
I barely hit you.

165
00:06:52,410 --> 00:06:54,970
I'll go easier on you next time.

166
00:06:57,530 --> 00:06:58,220
There, there.

167
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,759
(Zuixian House)

168
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:04,040
(The Best Massage Parlor)

169
00:07:04,730 --> 00:07:05,289
Mister,

170
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:06,699
enjoy the beer.

171
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:08,259
Eat, drink, and have fun.

172
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:09,969
If we weren't rivals,

173
00:07:09,970 --> 00:07:11,050
perhaps

174
00:07:11,580 --> 00:07:12,940
we would be good friends.

175
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:19,520
(Spend 5 taels, get 1 tael back)
Ladies and gentlemen,

176
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,460
we offer good discounts today!
Come take a look!

177
00:07:22,730 --> 00:07:24,050
Discounts!

178
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:37,610
Ladies and gentlemen,
come have a look.

179
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:39,379
We're offering discounts today.

180
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:40,900
This way, please.

181
00:07:43,850 --> 00:07:45,220
Spend five, get one back?

182
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:47,900
You're a true businesswoman, Miss Yan.

183
00:07:47,970 --> 00:07:49,529
I'm impressed.

184
00:07:49,530 --> 00:07:52,769
Your business sense impresses me even more.

185
00:07:52,770 --> 00:07:54,059
Naturally.

186
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:58,290
I've seen it all in the big cities.

187
00:07:59,650 --> 00:08:02,459
You're certainly well-traveled.

188
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:04,290
I'll have to learn

189
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:06,819
a thing or two from you.

190
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,289
I'm no expert.

191
00:08:08,290 --> 00:08:09,089
Honestly,

192
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:10,059
everything I know

193
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:12,209
I learned from Taobao.

194
00:08:12,210 --> 00:08:14,380
Go ask Taobao if you're curious.

195
00:08:14,410 --> 00:08:17,050
I've heard of Master Tao.

196
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:21,260
Wait a minute, Miss Yan.

197
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:26,140
Wasn't Tao Bao'er a woman?

198
00:08:28,090 --> 00:08:29,650
Silly me.

199
00:08:29,700 --> 00:08:31,140
I must be mistaken.

200
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:33,340
Sir,

201
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:34,569
this way.

202
00:08:34,570 --> 00:08:35,890
We're having a sale.

203
00:08:37,770 --> 00:08:40,370
Did you really think
I sent you here to do business?

204
00:08:41,170 --> 00:08:43,250
You've forgotten your mission.

205
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:43,689
I...

206
00:08:43,690 --> 00:08:44,700
I know.

207
00:08:48,860 --> 00:08:50,970
You've already made them suspicious.

208
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:52,890
Think about your brother.

209
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:55,340
Don't ruin my plans.

210
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,530
I...

211
00:08:57,110 --> 00:08:59,700
I won't compete
with Xiaoyao Pavilion anymore.

212
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:01,220
Please.

213
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:02,420
Please.

214
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,509
Let me see my brother.

215
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:05,720
Please!

216
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:09,370
You're not in a position to bargain.

217
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:11,420
Until the mission is complete,

218
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:13,130
you won't see him.

219
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:17,879
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

220
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:20,279
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

221
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:25,719
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

222
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:30,079
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

223
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:32,479
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

224
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:35,039
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

225
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:40,719
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

226
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:46,280
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

227
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:52,600
♪Funny moments never stop♪

228
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:55,440
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

229
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:59,799
♪Yet through every up and down♪

230
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,760
♪We create miracles♪

231
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,520
♪From naive youths♪

232
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:07,279
♪To legendary heroes♪

233
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:09,199
♪This journey♪

234
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:13,239
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

235
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:15,760
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

236
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:21,120
♪Let's create♪

237
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:31,080
♪A legend of our own♪
